Class ConnectedAttributes

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,AttributeMetadata>

    public abstract class ConnectedAttributes
extends java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,AttributeMetadata>
    Represents a map of exposed attributes to the adapter.

    This is an utility class and can be used to organize connected attributes in some types of custom adapters.
